00:00:43.840 --> 00:00:48.180
So Steve Nash is by no means the most athletic
guard to ever enter the NBA I'm not even sure

00:00:48.180 --> 00:00:53.399
he can dunk but what he does have is a series
of tricks and crafty moves that are awesome

00:00:53.399 --> 00:00:55.250
